#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn45.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.27:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Micchattavagga "
msgstr "3. The Wrong Way "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Kumbhasutta "
msgstr "27. Pots "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.21, sc1
msgctxt "sn45.27:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.27:1.2"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kumbho anādhāro suppavattiyo hoti, sādhāro duppavattiyo hoti; "
msgstr "“A pot without a stand is easy to overturn, but if it has a stand it’s hard to overturn. "

msgctxt "sn45.27:1.3"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, cittaṃ anādhāraṃ suppavattiyaṃ hoti, sādhāraṃ duppavattiyaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "In the same way, a mind without a stand is easy to overturn, but if it has a stand it’s hard to overturn. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.27:1.4"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, cittassa ādhāro? "
msgstr "And what’s the stand for the mind? "

msgctxt "sn45.27:1.5"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is: "

msgctxt "sn45.27:1.6"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "

msgctxt "sn45.27:1.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ cittassa ādhāro. "
msgstr "This is the stand for the mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.27:1.8"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kumbho anādhāro suppavattiyo hoti, sādhāro duppavattiyo hoti; "
msgstr "A pot without a stand is easy to overturn, but if it has a stand it’s hard to overturn. "

msgctxt "sn45.27:1.9"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, cittaṃ anādhāraṃ suppavattiyaṃ hoti, sādhāraṃ duppavattiyaṃ hotī”ti. "
msgstr "In the same way, a mind without a stand is easy to overturn, but if it has a stand it’s hard to overturn.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.27:1.10"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

